  "detailed_description": "One S'More is a charming 3D single-player puzzle game that combines cute cartoon visuals with challenging gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/cae3e2448e454e6441652ab04d248d72.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/cae3e2448e454e6441652ab04d248d72.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Lead your marshmallow buddy through a world full of floating cookies, waffles, jelly and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/96bfb4f3360641cb455dddea3cf752b6.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/96bfb4f3360641cb455dddea3cf752b6.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>A simple click can split islands, break cookies and set the world into motion to rearrange entire levels, bringing the marshmallow closer to its goal of being squished between two chocolate cookies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/ea1965a609217cfc33b82f8917ce5ed0.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/ea1965a609217cfc33b82f8917ce5ed0.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Easy-to-learn mechanics serve as the base for a ton of unique levels with increasing difficulty.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/2bed3e1821dfaceafdb4e8c195a22f71.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/2bed3e1821dfaceafdb4e8c195a22f71.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Still hungry for more after completing the campaign? You can create your own levels in the editor and share them with the community!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/bc4b8be272b16ecc5c80c82981d99195.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/bc4b8be272b16ecc5c80c82981d99195.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "One S'More is a charming 3D single-player puzzle game that combines cute cartoon visuals with challenging gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/cae3e2448e454e6441652ab04d248d72.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/cae3e2448e454e6441652ab04d248d72.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Lead your marshmallow buddy through a world full of floating cookies, waffles, jelly and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/96bfb4f3360641cb455dddea3cf752b6.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/96bfb4f3360641cb455dddea3cf752b6.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>A simple click can split islands, break cookies and set the world into motion to rearrange entire levels, bringing the marshmallow closer to its goal of being squished between two chocolate cookies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/ea1965a609217cfc33b82f8917ce5ed0.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/ea1965a609217cfc33b82f8917ce5ed0.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Easy-to-learn mechanics serve as the base for a ton of unique levels with increasing difficulty.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/2bed3e1821dfaceafdb4e8c195a22f71.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/2bed3e1821dfaceafdb4e8c195a22f71.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Still hungry for more after completing the campaign? You can create your own levels in the editor and share them with the community!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/bc4b8be272b16ecc5c80c82981d99195.poster.avif?t=1728401449\" width=624 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452930/extras/bc4b8be272b16ecc5c80c82981d99195.webm?t=1728401449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
